org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.server.namenode

Class SaveNamespaceContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.server.namenode.SaveNamespaceContext

  • @InterfaceAudience.Private
public class SaveNamespaceContext
extends Object
    Context for an ongoing SaveNamespace operation. This class allows cancellation, and also is responsible for accumulating failed storage directories.
